{
  "stem": "26672.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All our ambition was to be able to stand on our own feet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very difficult for us to settle down to-- to-- to do things, to be told what to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were men already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Windermere, when they were passing through beginning, when they were passing school the meals, we were sitting at long benches, long tables.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they couldn't understand, as we were passing through the meals from beginning table to the end, kept on going around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As we were given the meal, we put it on the table.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't realize that we were going to get meals in the evening, and in the next morning, and we don't have to hide.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We must have been very difficult people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some were nurses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some where, I'm sure, leaders of groups of certain-- I remember distinctly, [NON-ENGLISH] was a religious man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Israel Cohen, who was a teacher [INAUDIBLE] for years, who lives now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His present wife that wasn't married then was a nurse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had laryngitis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We started singing, and eventually voice broke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had terrible trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It broke on Yom Kippur, I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had service.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were singing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she nursed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She gave me steam towels and steam, to bring me back to-- yeah, they were wonderful people, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I registered-- well I went-- I registered myself, eventually got to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think from Highbury New Park, I went back to Gateshead, and came back to London.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember where I stayed in London.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, anyway, I registered myself, and got to Israel, [INAUDIBLE] Palestine [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I had to wait.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
